lead_paragraph: Norwich City snatched a thrilling 3-2 victory over fellow relegation contenders Newcastle United with a last-gasp strike by their Swedish full back Martin Olsson in a thriller at Carrow Road on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Late Olsson Strike Gives Norwich 3-2 Win Over Newcastle
